OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with hill fog across the
OL,6,FPennines, and light rain gradually
OL,7,Feasing but giving way to showers.
OL,8,FElsewhere, mostly cloudy to start but
OL,9,Fsome bright spells develop later.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy with rain
OL,13,Flikely in the west and over high
OL,14,Fground, more settled and drier in the
OL,15,Feast. Winds easing slightly but breezy
OL,16,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
