OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy and breezy for much of
OL,6,Fthe period with spells of rain at
OL,7,Ftimes, mostly affecting western hills
OL,8,Fwith drier conditions further east.
OL,9,FTemperatures becoming rather warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,12,Fand Tuesday, cloudy with spells of
OL,13,Frain at times, mostly affecting
OL,14,Fwestern hills with drier conditions
OL,15,Ffurther east. Wednesday becoming drier
OL,16,Fand sunnier. Temperatures becoming
OL,17,Frather warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
